# Title: Potential Rcdll.DLL Sideloading
# Author: X__Junior (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-03-13
# Level: high
# Description: Detects potential DLL sideloading of rcdll.dll
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1574.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/image_load/image_load_side_load_rcdll.yml

ImageLoaded="*\\rcdll.dll" NOT (ImageLoaded IN ("C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Visual Studio\\*", "C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Windows Kits\\*"))